      </article>
      <article class="card process-card process-card-premium">
        <span class="process-step">02</span>
        <h3>Grade the outcome</h3>
        <p>Keep profit, loss, and bankroll movement tied to the original bet so your record stays consistent.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card process-card process-card-premium">
        <span class="process-step">03</span>
